    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "EFFECTIVE\nAUGUST 1, 1956\nTRANS-\nCANADA\nAIR LINES\nSYSTEM TIMETABLE\nFly\nTGA\nTHE MAPLE LEAF ROUTE\nTCA flies on your\nLOCAL TIME!\nServing\nCANADA • U.S.A.\nUNITED KINGDOM and EUROPE\nBERMUDA-CARIBBEAN\nand NASSAU",
      "Fly\nTCA\nOne of the World's Great Airlines\nGOOSE BAY\nVANCOUVER\nST. JOHN'S\nQEA \u0026 CPAL TO HONOLULU, AUSTRALIA, NEW ZEALAND AND THE ORI\nYARMOUT\nBAKEROSS\nPORT OF SPAIN\nTCA MILEAGES\nATLANTIC SERVICES — see page 10\nDUSSELDORF — LONDON, ENGLAND..\nSOUTHERN SERVICES — see page 12\nBERMUDA — BARBADOS\nTORONTO — TAMIA.\nTAMPA - KINGSION.\nDOMESTIC SERVICES -\nST. JOHN'S — HALIFAX.\nMUNIKCAL\nMONT KEAL - TOKONIO\nSASATOON — EDMONTON\nWINNIPEG - CALGARY.\nsee pages 6-7-8-9\nKIO DE JAN\nTOKONIO - WINDSOR/DETROI\nTORONTO - NEW TORK.\nSEATTLE TACOMA — VICTORIA\nBOSTON — HALIFAX....\nTCA}\nLEGEND\nTCA SERVICES\nOTHER AIR LINES\nTIME ZONES\nServes over 60 communities\nthroughout 23,000 route miles\nTRANS- CANADA AIR LINES"
    ],
